description:
The AC-13 cable can be supplied to any length and terminated to suit the customer's connector requirements. Please contact us to discuss your individual requirements.

Standard Technical Features

Mechanical:
• Cable Diameter: 18 mm 
• Weight in Air: 500 kg/km 
• Weight in Seawater: 300 kg/km 
• Bending Radius: 230 mm Static, 320 mm Dynamic 
• Colour: Yellow 

Construction:
• Core: 1 off coaxial, 2 twisted pairs 1.34 mm squared, 1 off screened quad 0.22 mm squared with drainwire, 1 off screened twisted pair 0.5 mm squared with drainwire, 2 off conductors 1.00 mm squared 
• Screening: Overall screen of alum. tape plus drainwire 
• Armouring: Single Layer 0.8 mm (Steel) 
• Outer Jacket: Polyurethane 
• Filler: Self-vulcanising compound 
• Filler Jacket: PVC, diameter 13.5 mm
